      <h1 class="title is-3 has-text-centered">About Minus 1</h1>

      <p class="content"> Minus 1 is a tactical assistant for gamers. The
      website hosts the strategy builder. The windows desktop app(work in
      progress) is used to interact with the strategies. Its purpose is be to 
      assist tacticians during a match. Minus 1 intended for team based strategy
      games however it compatible with any game.
      </p>

      <p class="content">
        Within the website someone or a team can create and store a strategy
        that outlines orders for each player. This strategy can be simple or
         extremely complex. When the game starts each  player will receive 
         individual orders (this will be through audio) from the desktop 
         client. Interacting with the app will be done though speech.
      </p>
